rComments: This is the best professor ever. He just gave everyone in our class 90s as long as we proved we could say "Oya". Seriously, this is the coolest guy I've ever met - if you like free marks.
So rude. Made us buy this huge textbook and we never used it!
Avoid at all costs! It's impossible to understand what he says in class and the homework is even worse. He jumps back and forth through sections of the syllabus. Made my life hell!

He's great if you actually listen to what he's saying rather than just hear the accent, see the suit and be intimidated into thinking, wow this guy is a REAL univ level professor... You can tell he knows his material really well and it shows in his graet explanations.

I think I hear a fog horn...BORINGGGG!!! This guy doesnt know what he's talking about. He looks at his laptop every sentence he speaks...it's like he knows nothing. When he's teaching physics, your best friend might as well be your textbook because your mind will wander in his class and may never come back.
